                     <interp inst="t18220522-117-person1082" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220522-117-person1082" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. About half-past seven o'clock in the morning, I saw the prisoner with another in Harley-street; the prisoner went down the area of No. 79; then came up, stood about fives minutes and stooped, and I missed a pint pot off the rails; he went down again, and on his return took a quart pot off, wrapped it in a cloth and put it in his bosom. I followed and took it out and one from his hat.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner pleaded distress.</p>
